<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Donation Page</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/donation.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header class="header">
        <h1>Donation Page</h1>
    </header>

    <section class="donation-grid">
        <div class="donation-card">
            <h2>Hackhound Club Hackathon</h2>
            <p>Support the Hackhound Club in organizing the annual hackathon. Your donation will help cover event costs, participant swag, and more.</p>
            <button onclick="donate('Hackhound Club Hackathon')">Donate Now</button>
        </div>
        
        <div class="donation-card">
            <h2>Green Earth Initiative</h2>
            <p>Contribute to environmental conservation efforts with the Green Earth Initiative. Funds will be used for tree planting and waste reduction programs.</p>
            <button onclick="donate('Green Earth Initiative')">Donate Now</button>
        </div>
        
        <div class="donation-card">
            <h2>Literacy for All Campaign</h2>
            <p>Help improve literacy rates by supporting the Literacy for All Campaign. Donations will fund educational resources and training programs.</p>
            <button onclick="donate('Literacy for All Campaign')">Donate Now</button>
        </div>
        
        <div class="donation-card">
            <h2>Tech for Kids Foundation</h2>
            <p>Support the Tech for Kids Foundation in providing technology and educational resources to underprivileged children.</p>
            <button onclick="donate('Tech for Kids Foundation')">Donate Now</button>
        </div>

        <div class="donation-card">
            <h2>Veterans Support Fund</h2>
            <p>Assist veterans in transitioning back to civilian life by contributing to the Veterans Support Fund. Your donation will aid in job training and mental health services.</p>
            <button onclick="donate('Veterans Support Fund')">Donate Now</button>
        </div>
    </section>

    <script>
           function donate(eventName) {
        // Log the event or any logic before redirection
        console.log("Donating to: " + eventName);
        
        // Redirect to the donation page
        window.location.href = "/paymentGateway"; // Change "/donation-page" to the URL you want to link to
    }

    </script>
</body>
</html>

